---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Makeaway"
  description="A personal field guide for building a freer life through hiking, side projects, money, travel, and figuring things out along the way."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>A personal field guide for building a freer life.</h1>

    <p class="intro">
      Notes on hiking, escaping the rat race, side projects, money, travel,
      and figuring things out along the way.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="cards">
   
    <a class="card" href="/escape">
      <h2>Escape</h2>
      <p>
        Thoughts on work, burnout, freedom, and designing a life that feels
        more your own.
      </p>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="/outside">
      <h2>Outside</h2>
      <p>
        Hiking, camping, nature, gear, and the places that reset your brain.
      </p>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="/build">
      <h2>Build</h2>
      <p>
        Side projects, websites, experiments, and learning new skills by
        actually making things.
      </p>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="/game">
      <h2>Game</h2>
      <p>
        Runes of the way. A small game where you collect runes to make your way out of the maze.
      </p>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="/money">
      <h2>Money</h2>
      <p>
        Investing, dividends, options, and the long road toward more
        independence.
      </p>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="/articles">
      <h2>Articles</h2>
      <p>
        Longer notes, ideas, research, and writeups from the Makeaway project.
      </p>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="/land">
      <h2>Land</h2>
      <p>
        Research notes for the Camden County land, A-F zoning, family compound
        possibilities, and homestead due diligence.
      </p>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="/education">
      <h2>Education</h2>
      <p>
        Useful learning resources, tools, guides, and websites for building a
        freer, more capable life.
      </p>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="/recipes">
      <h2>Recipes</h2>
      <p>
        Simple meals, camp cooking, homestead recipes, and practical food ideas
        for building a more self-sufficient life.
      </p>
      <a class="card" href="/guides/">
       
       <h2>Guides</h2>
      <p>
        Practical reference guides, training material, and useful resources for
        building skills, learning systems, and becoming more capable.
       </p>
        </a>
    </a>
        <a class="card" href="/garden">
      <h2>Garden</h2>
      <p>
        Practical garden notes, growing experiments, seed starting, soil work,
        harvest lessons, and simple ways to grow more of your own food.
      </p>
      <a
  class="card"
  href="https://www.reddit.com/r/Makeaway/"
  target="_blank"
  rel="noopener noreferrer"
>
  <h2>Community</h2>
  <p>
    Join r/Makeaway to share projects, ask questions, post progress, and connect
    with people building a more practical and independent life.
  </p>
</a>
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>